- Who?

71
00:07:15,478 --> 00:07:17,139
Your driver.
- Sardar Makhan Singh

72
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:20,113
Please wait in the car.
I'll go and fetch your luggage

73
00:07:45,375 --> 00:07:47,366
This is the best locality of Paris

74
00:07:47,643 --> 00:07:50,237
And I've engaged this flat
specially for you

75
00:07:50,446 --> 00:07:53,677
How about you?
- I have an apartment near the office

76
00:08:00,089 --> 00:08:03,320
This is Honey.
She's studying in Paris

77
00:08:03,993 --> 00:08:07,394
I thought you'd need a companion

78
00:08:10,033 --> 00:08:14,163
I have an important meeting,
if I'm not needed here, dear

79
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:18,372
Go ahead.
- Deepa mustn't have any trouble...

80
00:08:18,808 --> 00:08:21,038
You needn't say that, uncle.
- See you tomorrow morning

81
00:08:27,417 --> 00:08:31,114
I'm terribly tired.
I'd like to take a bath first

82
00:08:31,287 --> 00:08:33,346
Where's the bathroom?
- Right ahead

83
00:08:33,623 --> 00:08:35,284
Hot water, towels...
everything's ready

84
00:08:37,326 --> 00:08:41,126
The driver's bringing my luggage.
Please fetch my dressing gown

85
00:08:41,431 --> 00:08:42,693
It's right at the top.
- Okay

86
00:08:43,132 --> 00:08:44,599
Would you like something to drink?
- Coffee

87
00:09:00,116 --> 00:09:02,914
Mistress, I've brought your luggage.
- Keep it there

88
00:09:03,719 --> 00:09:06,654
And what do I see? A dream!

89
00:09:07,723 --> 00:09:11,194
Beautiful! Very beautiful!
You're too good to be true!

90
00:09:11,194 --> 00:09:13,321
What did you say?
- Solid! You're for real!

91
00:09:14,564 --> 00:09:16,464
Honey...
- Coming!

92
00:09:18,367 --> 00:09:24,431
Honey! What a sweet name...
like the petha from Agra!

93
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:29,842
Did I hear you say something?
- I want to

94
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:34,109
I know today what
hate at first sight means!

95
00:09:34,450 --> 00:09:36,816
Nut!
- I think you like me

96
00:09:40,223 --> 00:09:42,248
What happened?
- Come here. Quick

97
00:09:48,798 --> 00:09:51,198
I open this door and
guess what I see

98
00:09:51,534 --> 00:09:52,330
A peeping tom?
- No

99
00:09:54,103 --> 00:09:55,092
Look down there

100
00:10:01,144 --> 00:10:04,080
That's perfectly normal.
- Out in the open?

101
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,844
Out here, they romance every where
and every time

102
00:10:09,952 --> 00:10:13,149
It's something Paris is famous for.
If you don't fall in love in Paris...

103
00:10:13,389 --> 00:10:15,789
you won't fall in love
anywhere else in the world

104
00:10:16,125 --> 00:10:19,686
But love, you've got to find.
- In Paris?

105
00:10:20,663 --> 00:10:24,292
In Paris, love finds you
- Really?

106
00:10:24,867 --> 00:10:31,295
Honey, I always have a dream...
an unfinished dream

107
00:10:31,574 --> 00:10:33,303
Of love?
- Yes

108
00:10:33,576 --> 00:10:37,273
It isn't about lust or fancies.
It's a dream of true love

109
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:40,943
You mean you don't have a boyfriend?
- Why not?

110
00:10:43,753 --> 00:10:45,321
I have many.
- So what's wrong?

111
00:10:45,321 --> 00:10:50,059
But they love my wealth...
not me

112
00:10:50,059 --> 00:10:52,960
I've lost faith in lovers

113
00:10:54,697 --> 00:10:57,257
But nobody knows you here

114
00:10:57,867 --> 00:11:01,303
You can pretend to be
a simple, poor girl

115
00:11:01,804 --> 00:11:05,433
And if someone falls for a poor girl,
he'll be a true lover. Right?

116
00:11:19,722 --> 00:11:23,283
Please put this away safely.
I'll ask you for it, when I need it

117
00:11:23,659 --> 00:11:25,217
I'll keep it in the safe
at the office

118
00:11:25,661 --> 00:11:28,755
Another thing...
I'm a very poor girl

119
00:11:29,098 --> 00:11:31,362
This flat belongs to Honey,
and I'm her maid-servant

120
00:11:31,601 --> 00:11:32,625
Pardon me?

121
00:11:33,035 --> 00:11:36,232
That's what you will tell anyone
who asks you about me

122
00:11:36,572 --> 00:11:37,698
But...

123
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:40,734
That's a secret we can't
tell you about, uncle

124
00:11:41,911 --> 00:11:45,278
You may leave now.
- Very well. Here I go

125
00:11:48,384 --> 00:11:51,717
Makhan's late, Honey.
- Here I am

126
00:11:52,521 --> 00:11:54,989
I had to look in every nook
and corner of Paris...

127
00:11:55,291 --> 00:11:58,089
to find this dress of
an Indian maid-servant

128
00:11:58,794 --> 00:12:00,955
I'll try it on

129
00:12:02,398 --> 00:12:06,164
Try something, beautiful one.
- What?

130
00:12:06,302 --> 00:12:10,636
My love, I mean. I'm willing
to do anything for you

131
00:12:10,906 --> 00:12:16,640
Shut up, or you'll lose your job!
- For you, I'd even give up life!

132
00:12:17,213 --> 00:12:20,114
Look what I've got for you.
- Lipstick?

133
00:12:20,816 --> 00:12:22,408
Yes. Apply it on your lips

134
00:12:25,588 --> 00:12:26,680
That's something!

135
00:12:26,922 --> 00:12:32,053
Had I known you'd cling to me
after one little burst...

136
00:12:32,361 --> 00:12:35,421
I'd have bought
a dozen fire-crackers

137
00:12:35,731 --> 00:12:37,995
Cheat, rascal!
You dare do this!

138
00:12:38,234 --> 00:12:39,428
I'll fix you yet!

139
00:12:48,411 --> 00:12:50,936
Shekhar?
- What's this?

140
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:57,412
Daddy, since when you have
started dealing in jewelry?

141
00:12:57,687 --> 00:13:00,713
Put that back in there.
- Is that fake or real?

142
00:13:01,223 --> 00:13:03,885
It belongs to my mistress.
- Mistress?

143
00:13:04,226 --> 00:13:09,493
Yes. Deepa, she's here
on a tour of Paris

144
00:13:09,865 --> 00:13:15,360
I'll take her around Paris, daddy.
Just introduce me to her

145
00:13:15,705 --> 00:13:17,730
Never. You're not worthy of it

146
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:20,904
Didn't I ask you not to come here?
- I'm in need, daddy

147
00:13:21,444 --> 00:13:23,776
What is it?
- I need 200,000 rupees

148
00:13:24,046 --> 00:13:26,378
200,000?
- I've got to repay some debts

149
00:13:26,716 --> 00:13:30,550
Debts of liquor and gambling?
- It's a question of my life, daddy

150
00:13:30,753 --> 00:13:34,746
I have nothing to do with it.
- I'm your only son, daddy!

151
00:13:35,191 --> 00:13:39,218
Our relationship ended when I got to
know of your misdeeds

152
00:13:39,762 --> 00:13:43,391
Please, daddy! You must help me!
You have millions!

153
00:13:43,966 --> 00:13:48,300
The money belongs to Deepa's father.
I'm only their manager

154
00:13:48,671 --> 00:13:50,332
Daddy, I might lose my life!

155
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:56,474
Shekhar, I have no sympathies
for a gambler. You may go now

156
00:14:04,787 --> 00:14:07,221
Where will I look for her?

157
00:14:07,423 --> 00:14:09,414
My word!

158
00:14:13,696 --> 00:14:18,258
Who's that?
- Why are you there, Your Majesty?

159
00:14:18,467 --> 00:14:20,901
I'm right here!
- What are you doing here?

160
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:23,530
I asked you to look for Deepa.
- You're right

161
00:14:23,873 --> 00:14:26,603
From the Eiffel Tower, I was
looking for her.

162
00:14:26,942 --> 00:14:29,467
I saw you and I came
down immediately

163
00:14:31,347 --> 00:14:34,077
Where could she have gone?
- I'll tell you

164
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:37,314
She has gone looking
for her true love

165
00:15:39,048 --> 00:15:40,913
I can speak a bit of Hindustani

166
00:15:43,185 --> 00:15:47,815
An Indian guy is my friend.
- Wonderful. What is your name?

167
00:15:53,028 --> 00:15:54,586
My name is Deepa

168
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:57,797
Deepa! Wonderful!

169
00:16:05,508 --> 00:16:10,070
A beautiful girl like you isn't
in love, nor married. Why?

170
00:16:11,413 --> 00:16:15,611
Boys in India look for money
in marriage

171
00:16:21,490 --> 00:16:23,321
No. They're all very greedy

172
00:16:26,629 --> 00:16:28,790
Cheats! Frauds!

173
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:41,876
What?
- You're beautiful and I'm in love

174
00:16:44,914 --> 00:16:48,577
I'm very poor?
- Eh?

175
00:16:51,020 --> 00:16:54,581
Good! I'm poor too.
No Mama, no Papa

176
00:16:55,925 --> 00:17:00,021
Aren't you married?
- Not married

177
00:17:00,496 --> 00:17:02,794
You and I will marry.
- I must leave now

178
00:17:03,465 --> 00:17:04,989
Leave? Will you come tomorrow?

179
00:17:05,734 --> 00:17:07,133
Sure, I will

180
00:17:07,603 --> 00:17:08,695
I will too!

181
00:17:51,447 --> 00:17:54,143
Photographer! Where have you
been all these days?

182
00:17:55,084 --> 00:17:57,382
I want an Indian dress. Quick!

183
00:17:58,220 --> 00:17:59,209
What do you want?

184
00:17:59,822 --> 00:18:02,313
A dress! I want to be
an Indian Maharaja

185
00:18:03,292 --> 00:18:06,557
An Indian Maharaja?
Are you in your senses?

186
00:18:06,862 --> 00:18:11,492
I'm not! I learnt Hindustani from you
and met a beautiful Indian girl

187
00:18:12,001 --> 00:18:14,128
I've fallen in love with her!

188
00:18:16,772 --> 00:18:19,764
What's her name?
- Deepa

189
00:18:20,142 --> 00:18:22,702
A look at her, and my heart skipped
a beat. I'm going to marry her

190
00:18:23,212 --> 00:18:27,239
Marry her? Couldn't she
find an Indian boy?

191
00:18:27,583 --> 00:18:30,552
Indian boys lust for money.
- Says who?

192
00:18:31,020 --> 00:18:35,980
Deepa. They're frauds and cheats!
- Who's this insolent girl?

193
00:18:38,994 --> 00:18:40,188
Where are you meeting her again?

194
00:18:43,432 --> 00:18:46,068
Really? I've got to fix her...
I sure must!

195
00:18:46,068 --> 00:18:48,195
I want to be an Indian Maharaja!

196
00:19:19,635 --> 00:19:22,104
Deepa! Are you happy?

197
00:19:22,104 --> 00:19:26,131
And who are you?
- An Indian Maharaja!

198
00:19:26,408 --> 00:19:28,876
We're going to marry, okay?

199
00:20:22,531 --> 00:20:24,829
I'm not their father!

200
00:21:16,285 --> 00:21:18,014
Lady...

201
00:21:20,289 --> 00:21:24,555
Because of one man, you have a
wrong impression of all Frenchmen

202
00:21:25,294 --> 00:21:29,060
You said you're French.
- Sure. I live in France

203
00:21:29,898 --> 00:21:33,334
But you speak Hindustani?
- As well as you do

204
00:21:33,669 --> 00:21:36,839
Spent twenty years in your country.
Are you from Lucknow?

205
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,830
No. From Delhi.
- I see

206
00:21:39,007 --> 00:21:41,100
My father was a professor
of French in Lucknow

207
00:21:41,210 --> 00:21:42,541
I see

208
00:21:43,178 --> 00:21:45,237
Your name?
- Deepa

209
00:21:45,614 --> 00:21:48,549
Lovely name... you are, too!

210
00:21:49,117 --> 00:21:50,886
On a pleasure trip in Paris?
- Yes, no...

211
00:21:50,886 --> 00:21:54,913
I'm here with my mistress.
I'm a poor maidservant

212
00:21:55,257 --> 00:21:59,057
Strange. When I was in India,
maid-servants didn't speak English

213
00:21:59,461 --> 00:22:03,192
Anyway, we're all equal in Paris.
There is no discrimination

214
00:22:03,532 --> 00:22:05,300
To prove that we must have
some coffee together

215
00:22:05,300 --> 00:22:09,464
No, I've got to go.
- But I must do something for you

216
00:22:09,738 --> 00:22:11,899
Why?
- To dispel doubts...

217
00:22:12,241 --> 00:22:15,301
that Frenchmen aren't good human beings
- That's what my first experience was

218
00:22:15,677 --> 00:22:17,338
So you must have another experience

219
00:22:32,261 --> 00:22:33,489
What did she say?

220
00:22:35,497 --> 00:22:39,134
She says, only fortunate men
have beautiful wives

221
00:22:39,134 --> 00:22:41,898
What?
- Do not take offense

222
00:22:42,104 --> 00:22:44,868
She thought I'm married, too,
although I'm not

223
00:22:47,676 --> 00:22:51,043
I haven't come across a girl who
isn't hankering for money

224
00:22:51,380 --> 00:22:52,711
What do you mean?
- No offense meant...

225
00:22:52,915 --> 00:22:57,716
but girls are generally very selfish.
- Boys are the ones who are selfish

226
00:22:58,020 --> 00:23:01,217
I know them all very well.
- Maybe you do

227
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:05,185
But you don't know French boys.
- Something special about them?

228
00:23:05,594 --> 00:23:08,427
Yes. They could die
for the girls they love

229
00:23:10,499 --> 00:23:13,161
When they fall in love, they
follow the girl for an eternity

230
00:23:14,736 --> 00:23:16,795
Don't you follow me, mister.
It won't be good for you

231
00:23:17,105 --> 00:23:19,630
Why must I? Strange girl!
You haven't even asked me my name...

232
00:23:19,908 --> 00:23:22,274
I'm not at all interested!

233
00:24:19,001 --> 00:24:20,901
"Ask me..."

234
00:24:21,703 --> 00:24:23,933
"what my name is"

235
00:24:24,673 --> 00:24:26,504
"Give me a loving look..."

236
00:24:27,542 --> 00:24:29,442
"and ask me what I seek"

237
00:24:29,911 --> 00:24:35,577
"Don't meet me after that,
if you don't want to..."

238
