in the world

1226
02:04:17,574 --> 02:04:20,372
No, you can't be anybody
but my daughter

1227
02:04:20,744 --> 02:04:22,974
Why not? I'm Suzy

1228
02:04:23,213 --> 02:04:25,078
I'm known at every
night club of Europe

1229
02:04:25,415 --> 02:04:27,815
Nightclubs? What do you do there?

1230
02:04:28,118 --> 02:04:30,018
I sing and dance
and make money!

1231
02:04:30,320 --> 02:04:32,049
No!
- Why not?

1232
02:04:32,456 --> 02:04:35,892
It is my profession.
Any more questions?

1233
02:04:36,193 --> 02:04:38,684
Yes. Why did you pose as Deepa
and stay here?

1234
02:04:40,430 --> 02:04:43,831
Sam, I want to have a
word with you in privacy

1235
02:04:44,134 --> 02:04:45,795
Where is Deepa?
- I don't know

1236
02:04:46,169 --> 02:04:48,467
Damodar, telephone the
police immediately

1237
02:04:50,774 --> 02:04:53,368
You're right. I made a mistake

1238
02:04:53,744 --> 02:04:56,110
My daughter could never be
a dancing girl

1239
02:04:56,613 --> 02:05:00,777
Hand her over to the police, Shyam!
- Do you want to see Deepa alive?

1240
02:05:01,618 --> 02:05:03,677
D'you know where Deepa is?
- Yes, I do

1241
02:05:03,920 --> 02:05:06,320
If you want to find out,
just come with me

1242
02:05:11,461 --> 02:05:13,156
Don't inform the police
till I return

1243
02:05:32,816 --> 02:05:34,044
Why have you brought me here?

1244
02:05:34,451 --> 02:05:37,511
Because this is the crossroad

1245
02:05:38,822 --> 02:05:40,653
You'll find it easier
to choose your path

1246
02:05:41,024 --> 02:05:43,117
What does that mean?
- Mean?

1247
02:05:43,927 --> 02:05:45,724
Come, I'll show you

1248
02:05:51,635 --> 02:05:56,663
Sam, before I met you, I spent
my life in night-clubs...

1249
02:05:56,907 --> 02:06:01,344
displaying my body to lustful
and disgusting men

1250
02:06:01,845 --> 02:06:06,805
It was after I met you that I realized
there's another meaning to life

1251
02:06:07,317 --> 02:06:08,341
What are you getting at?

1252
02:06:09,152 --> 02:06:14,920
I've fallen in love with you, Sam.
- And you know I'm in love with Deepa

1253
02:06:16,126 --> 02:06:18,788
And you want her to remain alive?
- Where is she?

1254
02:06:21,465 --> 02:06:24,332
That's something only I know

1255
02:06:25,135 --> 02:06:29,265
And you want a price to tell me?
- Naturally

1256
02:06:29,473 --> 02:06:31,441
How much do you want?
200,000? Half a million?

1257
02:06:31,708 --> 02:06:34,905
I want your love. That's all

1258
02:06:37,647 --> 02:06:40,582
Please accept me.
I give you my word...

1259
02:06:41,118 --> 02:06:43,712
Deepa will return safely
to her father

1260
02:06:45,222 --> 02:06:48,851
Aren't you his father?
- That man's a stranger to me!

1261
02:06:49,226 --> 02:06:51,217
I've never seen him
or stayed with him!

1262
02:06:51,528 --> 02:06:53,996
Have you no sympathies for your sister?
- No!

1263
02:06:54,398 --> 02:06:57,458
I've never known her as my sister.
- And now that you know...

1264
02:06:57,667 --> 02:06:59,157
you're bargaining with me
for her life?

1265
02:07:00,003 --> 02:07:01,095
Only for love

1266
02:07:01,872 --> 02:07:05,569
With your love, I want
to start life afresh

1267
02:07:06,376 --> 02:07:10,972
I want to belong to you, Sam.
- You're not worth it

1268
02:07:11,214 --> 02:07:13,580
Why not? What's the difference
between Deepa and me?

1269
02:07:13,784 --> 02:07:15,411
There's one hell of a difference!
In your shoes...

1270
02:07:15,685 --> 02:07:17,619
she'd have laid down her life
to save her sister!

1271
02:07:18,088 --> 02:07:22,024
The difference between you and Deepa
is what is between real and fake

1272
02:07:22,459 --> 02:07:25,758
As much difference as there is
between light and darkness

1273
02:07:26,096 --> 02:07:27,859
Between a noble man
and a scoundrel!

1274
02:07:28,165 --> 02:07:29,723
Where is Deepa?
Tell me!

1275
02:07:31,034 --> 02:07:33,901
If you change your mind,
come to my hotel

1276
