Wait here. I'll change
and return in a moment

1310
02:12:24,834 --> 02:12:26,495
Sit down, Sam

1311
02:12:49,792 --> 02:12:52,090
What have you decided?

1312
02:12:54,163 --> 02:12:56,358
I'll marry you

1313
02:13:00,636 --> 02:13:03,127
Without any conditions?
- You know

1314
02:13:09,679 --> 02:13:11,169
Will you undo the zip, please?

1315
02:13:14,083 --> 02:13:18,577
I want you to promise me that Deepa
will return safely

1316
02:13:19,355 --> 02:13:22,586
Is that all? You want
nothing else from me?

1317
02:13:25,428 --> 02:13:31,799
This is exactly why I love you, Sam.
You want nothing from me

1318
02:13:32,335 --> 02:13:35,532
You wanted to marry me.
And I'm willing

1319
02:13:35,871 --> 02:13:36,735
That's enough

1320
02:13:45,815 --> 02:13:49,376
What I sought from you was love.
Not pity!

1321
02:13:54,090 --> 02:13:58,117
I'll be in your arms all my life...
but Deepa will live in your heart

1322
02:13:58,594 --> 02:14:00,357
All my life, I'll have the feeling...

1323
02:14:00,596 --> 02:14:02,530
that you accepted me
out of helplessness

1324
02:14:05,935 --> 02:14:08,870
Maybe I'm rotten and cheap.
But I won't stoop...

1325
02:14:09,338 --> 02:14:12,432
to sell my emotions
in the name of marriage

1326
02:14:12,808 --> 02:14:14,139
You may go now

1327
02:14:32,061 --> 02:14:34,393
I'm sorry, I couldn't
get Suzy to agree

1328
02:14:35,297 --> 02:14:39,097
She didn't tell me Deepa's whereabouts.
- I told you to inform the police

1329
02:14:39,402 --> 02:14:41,870
That will endanger her life.
- Her life is already in danger

1330
02:14:43,272 --> 02:14:46,730
I wonder where my daughter is?

1331
02:14:48,444 --> 02:14:51,845
To have her back, I can even
give away all my wealth

1332
02:14:53,082 --> 02:14:55,107
I agree to every condition
those gangsters have

1333
02:14:55,651 --> 02:14:58,677
I'm willing to pay any price
to have Deepa back!

1334
02:14:59,055 --> 02:15:01,250
We only want a million dollars

1335
02:15:01,957 --> 02:15:02,981
Who?

1336
02:15:03,659 --> 02:15:04,956
Haven't you recognized me, sir?

1337
02:15:05,494 --> 02:15:08,691
It's your old faithful servant.
Jaggu

1338
02:15:10,733 --> 02:15:11,563
Jaggu! You're still alive?

1339
02:15:12,101 --> 02:15:14,831
Sure, I am.
And so is your daughter

1340
02:15:15,438 --> 02:15:20,034
I wish she were dead!
The state I saw her in...

1341
02:15:20,276 --> 02:15:25,145
Whom did you see?
- Roopa. She calls herself Suzy now

1342
02:15:25,514 --> 02:15:29,280
Suzy? Where did you meet her?
- In Deepa's flat!

1343
02:15:31,420 --> 02:15:34,048
I see. I get it now.
- Ingrate! Scoundrel!

1344
02:15:34,356 --> 02:15:37,189
Where have you kept Deepa?
I'll hand you over to the police!

1345
02:15:38,794 --> 02:15:40,819
You've already lost a daughter

1346
02:15:41,597 --> 02:15:43,064
D'you want to lose
the other one too?

1347
02:15:43,532 --> 02:15:47,229
Jaggu, you know where Deepa is?
- Yes, I do

1348
02:15:47,803 --> 02:15:50,897
If Jack doesn't have a million dollars
by tomorrow evening...

1349
02:15:51,240 --> 02:15:53,731
Deepa won't be allowed to live.
- No!

1350
02:15:54,210 --> 02:15:58,647
Can we raise a million by tomorrow?
- We can

1351
02:15:58,948 --> 02:16:01,940
One moment. How can you prove
that Deepa's in your custody?

1352
02:16:02,318 --> 02:16:04,752
Proof? Here it is

1353
02:16:11,227 --> 02:16:12,592
It's Deepa's handwriting

1354
02:16:13,195 --> 02:16:15,891
Where and whom have I
to pay the money?

1355
02:16:16,098 --> 02:16:18,396
In a black suitcase, one of you
will carry a million dollars...

1356
02:16:18,701 --> 02:16:23,934
and come to the tower at Niagara Falls
at 5:00 p.m. Tomorrow

1357
02:16:24,373 --> 02:16:28,332
What happens then?
- You'll get to know once you're there

1358
02:17:23,399 --> 02:17:25,867
Now tell me...
where is Deepa?

1359
02:17:27,770 --> 02:17:29,567
Speak! Where is Deepa?

1360
02:17:30,873 --> 02:17:33,000
Stop it

1361
02:17:33,742 --> 02:17:36,506
He has fainted. We had better
hand him over to the police

1362
02:17:37,213 --> 02:17:40,842
Damodar, book a seat for me
on the flight to Canada

1363
02:17:41,283 --> 02:17:43,012
You won't be able to
handle those thugs

1364
02:17:43,385 --> 02:17:45,819
This isn't something for you.
Let me go instead

1365
02:17:46,188 --> 02:17:48,713
Let you go? How's that possible?

1366
02:17:49,291 --> 02:17:51,282
It has to do with my daughter's life

1367
02:17:55,197 --> 02:17:57,222
And your daughter
means the life to me

1368
02:19:08,637 --> 02:19:11,265
Look, isn't she your duplicate?

1369
02:19:11,807 --> 02:19:13,069
Absolutely

1370
02:19:13,409 --> 02:19:16,810
Seems as if I were looking at
my reflection in the mirror

1371
02:19:18,447 --> 02:19:20,972
I must leave now.
Jaggu will be calling any moment

1372
02:19:36,799 --> 02:19:38,426
Don't cry, Deepa

1373
02:19:42,037 --> 02:19:44,904
Who are you?
- Your twin sister

1374
02:19:45,441 --> 02:19:48,069
But I didn't have any sisters.
- You don't know

1375
02:19:48,444 --> 02:19:51,504
I didn't know it either.
It was your father who told me

1376
02:19:51,814 --> 02:19:54,374
Daddy? Where?
- In Paris

1377
02:19:55,084 --> 02:19:57,018
It was the first time
I was meeting my father

1378
02:19:57,886 --> 02:20:00,480
But he refused to accept me
as his daughter

1379
02:20:00,956 --> 02:20:02,321
Why?

1380
02:20:03,625 --> 02:20:08,221
Because I'm as rotten
as nice you are

1381
02:20:09,431 --> 02:20:10,989
Between you and me...

1382
02:20:11,567 --> 02:20:14,092
is the difference that
sets apart darkness and light

1383
02:20:16,205 --> 02:20:18,070
Sam was right

1384
02:20:18,540 --> 02:20:19,802
Do you know Sam?

1385
02:20:21,877 --> 02:20:25,142
I got to know him. Briefly

1386
02:20:26,181 --> 02:20:28,274
Never mind all that

1387
02:20:28,751 --> 02:20:30,912
Quickly wear my clothes
and get out of here

1388
02:20:31,387 --> 02:20:34,288
And you?
- Don't worry about me

1389
02:20:34,623 --> 02:20:35,851
Your life is in danger!

1390
02:20:36,759 --> 02:20:39,227
Must I endanger my sister's life
to save my own skin?

1391
02:20:39,661 --> 02:20:41,720
No, I can never do that

1392
02:20:42,197 --> 02:20:45,655
Go away, Deepa. Let's not argue.
- No, I'm not going!

1393
02:20:46,135 --> 02:20:50,902
Please, Deepa...
don't waste your love on me

1394
02:20:51,507 --> 02:20:52,838
I don't deserve it

1395
02:20:54,143 --> 02:20:58,341
I work for these gangsters.
- What?

1396
02:21:02,317 --> 02:21:05,343
Henceforth, you must hate me too

1397
02:21:06,789 --> 02:21:10,122
But before you go,
please embrace me, Deepa

1398
02:21:11,360 --> 02:21:13,760
Maybe I'll never have
the opportunity again

1399
02:21:17,366 --> 02:21:18,390
Come

1400
02:21:20,702 --> 02:21:24,468
My sister!

1401
02:21:24,907 --> 02:21:28,536
When you meet Shyam,
do tell him on my behalf...

1402
02:21:29,445 --> 02:21:34,542
one lives in darkness because
there's no one to show him light

1403
02:22:50,626 --> 02:22:52,924
Shekhar! You?

1404
02:22:53,795 --> 02:22:58,732
I've been sent by Deepa's father.
With a million dollars

1405
02:22:59,468 --> 02:23:01,698
You?
- Yes

1406
02:23:02,371 --> 02:23:03,895
To take Deepa back

1407
02:23:06,808 --> 02:23:10,835
