a fraud like you?

1408
02:23:11,747 --> 02:23:13,908
He has agreed to accept me
as his son-in-law

1409
02:23:17,486 --> 02:23:19,681
So you've cast a spell
on her father too!

1410
02:23:20,989 --> 02:23:24,015
Jack, you always took me
for a fool

1411
02:23:24,760 --> 02:23:27,923
You always threatened me
and pushed me around

1412
02:23:29,264 --> 02:23:33,394
And now you're a smart man?
- Yes

1413
02:23:34,336 --> 02:23:36,702
Okay, smartie.
Set the bag there

1414
02:23:39,508 --> 02:23:42,068
Give it to me.
- First call Deepa

1415
02:23:44,546 --> 02:23:49,540
I can take it away by force.
- You won't, because this is a deal

1416
02:23:50,018 --> 02:23:51,849
You want money.
And I want Deepa

1417
02:23:53,922 --> 02:23:58,916
You've indeed smartened up.
I'm beginning to get scared of you

1418
02:24:10,472 --> 02:24:12,133
Did you see that?
- Yes, Jack

1419
02:24:12,441 --> 02:24:14,341
She's just like me!
- Isn't she!

1420
02:24:15,277 --> 02:24:17,336
Shekhar, you've met Suzy?

1421
02:24:20,782 --> 02:24:23,945
I'll take a walk outside,
while you chat

1422
02:24:28,790 --> 02:24:32,226
Jack, please ask someone
to see me out, will you?

1423
02:25:16,538 --> 02:25:19,632
Keep an eye on him.
And just wait there

1424
02:25:23,945 --> 02:25:26,937
Who's the other man?
- Other man? Who's that?

1425
02:25:27,616 --> 02:25:31,484
He's carrying a black suitcase
and is waiting near the tower

1426
02:25:32,954 --> 02:25:34,444
Could be someone.
How'd I know?

1427
02:25:37,559 --> 02:25:40,050
Hand it over to me.
- Don't you trust me?

1428
02:25:40,595 --> 02:25:42,927
We don't even trust our fathers
in this business

1429
02:25:43,598 --> 02:25:44,826
Not yourself either

1430
02:26:05,954 --> 02:26:06,716
Hurry up!

1431
02:26:42,324 --> 02:26:43,552
Is that man still there?

1432
02:26:44,659 --> 02:26:47,025
Send him into the tunnel
immediately

1433
02:27:15,223 --> 02:27:17,919
Don't you dare make any noise.
Just come with me

1434
02:29:22,317 --> 02:29:25,081
Your old flame. Sam

1435
02:29:26,821 --> 02:29:29,119
He has always put
obstacles in my path

1436
02:29:29,624 --> 02:29:31,421
Today, I have him where I want him

1437
02:29:32,394 --> 02:29:34,191
Sam, go away!

1438
02:29:36,264 --> 02:29:40,132
I'm not Deepa! I'm Suzy!
Believe me!

1439
02:29:40,435 --> 02:29:41,925
I've helped Deepa escape!

1440
02:29:42,170 --> 02:29:46,266
She's waiting for you in Jack's boat.
Go away, Sam! Just escape!

1441
02:31:03,018 --> 02:31:05,213
What happened?
- Suzy's hurt, Makhan Singh!

1442
02:31:05,820 --> 02:31:07,754
Shekhar shot at her and escaped.
I'm going after him...

1443
02:31:08,056 --> 02:31:10,752
and she's lying unconscious there.
- I'll go and get the police

1444
02:31:10,992 --> 02:31:11,651
Hurry up!

1445
02:39:24,118 --> 02:39:26,712
